==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[corner]] [[kick]]'''

#{{soccer}}: A [[kick]] awarded to the [[attack]]ing team when the [[ball]] leaves the [[field]] of play by wholly crossing the [[goal line]] without a goal having been scored.  For the kick, the ball is placed within the [[corner arc]] closest to where the ball went out of play.

